080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08154501%2FF6tpBhfa0AArOS4-300x271.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08154501%2FF6tpBhfa0AArOS4-1024x923.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22309%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40CricCrazyJohns%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20I%20pondered%20on%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20for%20this%20regime%20to%20summon%20celebrities%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20Vishwaguru%20and%20how%20they%20had%20bartered%20away%20their%20souls%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20brute%20political%20power%2C%20by%20a%20happy%20stroke%20of%20serendipity%20I%20chanced%20upon%20a%20quote%20from%20the%20great%20Senegalese%20footballer%20Sadio%20Mane%20on%20his%20philosophy%20of%20life.%20In%20his%20own%20stirring%20words%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20resisted%20hunger%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20I%20survived%20wars%2C%20I%20played%20football%20barefoot%2C%20I%20had%20no%20education%20and%20many%20more%20things%2C%20but%20today%20with%20what%20I%20earn%20from%20football%20I%20can%20help%20my%20people.%20I%20built%20schools%2C%20a%20hospital%2C%20we%20offer%20clothes%2C%20shoes%20food%20to%20people%20living%20in%20extreme%20poverty.%20In%20addition%2C%20I%20give%2070%20euros%20per%20month%20to%20all%20people%20in%20a%20very%20poor%20region%20of%20Senegal.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20flaunt%20fancy%20cars%2C%20fancy%20villas%2C%20travel%2C%20let%20alone%20planes.%20I%E2%80%99d%20rather%20have%20my%20people%20get%20a%20bit%20of%20what%20life%20has%20given%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6my%20people%20get%20a%20bit%20of%20what%20life%20has%20given%20me.%E2%80%9D%20What%20a%20stark%20contrast%20from%20our%20famous%20persons%20who%20are%20so%20consumed%20in%20themselves%20and%20busy%20cashing%20in%20on%20their%20demigod%20status%20that%20they%20have%20forgotten%20that%20they%20owe%20a%20debt%20to%20society.%20It%20is%20sad%20because%20celebrities%20are%20respected%20community%20mentors%20with%20a%20greater%20influence%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20young%2C%20than%20religious%20or%20political%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENobody%20expects%20them%20to%20part%20with%20their%20money.%20But%2C%20like%20the%20great%20West%20Indian%2C%20Michael%20Holding%20observed%2C%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfun%20and%20games%E2%80%9D%2C%20celebrities%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20use%20their%20privileged%20position%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20laurels%20won%20but%20what%20you%20give%20back%20to%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoseph%20Campbell%20put%20it%20best%20with%20his%20simple%20but%20profound%20assertion%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20hero%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20given%20his%20or%20her%20life%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20oneself%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20celebrity%20has%20generally%20been%20reticent%2C%20if%20not%20downright%20uncaring%20of%20his%20social%20responsibilities.%20I%20had%20a%20theory%2C%20now%20dented%20by%20Mane%2C%20that%20the%20poorer%20a%20nation%2C%20the%20more%20solipsistic%20and%20self-seeking%20are%20its%20rich%20and%20famous%2C%20possibly%20because%20of%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20insecurity.%20Amid%20conspicuous%20and%20widespread%20deprivation%2C%20our%20celebrities%20tend%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20misery%20by%20bolting%20their%20ivory%20tower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20celebrities%20wield%20incredible%20social%20power.%20With%20millions%20of%20devotees%20hanging%20on%20to%20their%20every%20word%2C%20they%20are%20up%20there%20with%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leading%20opinion-makers.%20They%20can%20invigorate%20social%20justice%20campaigns%20with%20the%20power%20of%20their%20voices.%20Regrettably%2C%20most%20of%20them%20are%20self-obsessive.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Tendulkar.%20The%20greatest%20run%20getter%20in%20history%2C%20arguably%20the%20richest%20cricketer%2C%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20Sachin%20has%20exploited%20his%20stardom%20solely%20for%20hawking%20merchandise%20and%20for%20other%20less%20honourable%20purposes.%20He%20sought%20and%20obtained%20a%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20customs%20duty%20exemption%20on%20the%20Ferrari%20presented%20to%20him%20by%20Michael%20Schumacher%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ferrari%20company.%20More%20controversially%2C%20he%20allegedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fdrdo-officer-files-cbi-complaint-on-sanjay-narang-resort-sachin-tendulkar-denies-economic-interest%2Farticleshow%2F53291570.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etried%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20procurer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20his%20hotelier%20crony%20who%20had%20illegally%20encroached%20army%20cantonment%20land%2C%20but%20the%20then%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20Manohar%20Parrikar%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20play%20ball.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Sachin%20goes%20missing%20when%20it%20matters.%20He%20remained%20silent%20when%20the%20female%20wrestlers%20protesting%20sexual%20harassment%20sought%20his%20backing%2C%20and%20he%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20his%20former%20teammate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-jaffer-uttarakhand-coach-cricket-communalism%5C%22%3EWassim%20Jaffer%2C%20who%20was%20unjustly%20accused%20of%20communal%20bias%20by%20right-wing%20bigots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereas%20Anil%20Kumble%20showed%20character%20by%20coming%20out%20in%20su