ut%20questions%20being%20raised%20on%20civil%20liberties%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20Khan%20talked%20of%20cinema%20as%20a%20medium%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20humanity%E2%80%99s%20intense%20capacity%20for%20compassion%2C%20unity%20and%20brotherhood.%E2%80%9D%20A%20trifle%2C%20pussyfooted%20and%20oblique%2C%20but%20as%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20a%20penny%20is%20better%20than%20none!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20experience%20I%20know%20that%20our%20women%20are%20infinitely%20smarter%20than%20men%20and%20made%20of%20sterner%20stuff.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Emonths-long%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20of%20our%20internationally%20renowned%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20led%20by%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20against%20continual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpictures-phone-location-other-evidence-show-brij-bhushan-allegedly-making-advances%5C%22%3Esexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20most%20courageous%20face-off%20by%20women%20anywhere%20against%20a%20repressive%2C%20hostile%20government%20that%20used%20every%20sordid%20means%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20their%20knees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20despite%20coercive%20police%20brutality%2C%20waves%20of%20officially%20sponsored%20vandalism%20of%20their%20protest%20site%2C%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%20and%20vicious%20slander%2C%20these%20indomitable%20women%20stood%20their%20ground%2C%20eventually%20forcing%20this%20regime%20to%20initiate%20legal%20action%20against%20one%20of%20its%20own.%20By%20throwing%20down%20the%20gauntlet%20against%20a%20deeply%20ingrained%2C%20rotten%20culture%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20they%20spoke%20up%20for%20all%20the%20voiceless%20girls%20who%20cannot%20protect%