home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Channing%20Muller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202022%2C%20I%20flew%20to%20Chicago%20to%20run%20a%20marathon.%20I%20got%20to%20see%20so%20much%20of%20the%20city%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20amazing.%20When%20I%20returned%20to%20Tennessee%2C%20my%20patience%20just%20kind%20of%20hit%20the%20roof%20%E2%80%94%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20something%20else%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20a%20more%20liberal%20state%20and%20in%20a%20bigger%20city.%20Chicago%20checked%20my%20boxes.%20It%20has%20all%20the%20things%20you%20want%20in%20a%20metropolitan%20city%20%E2%80%94%20activities%20and%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20more%20approachable%20than%20a%20place%20like%20New%20York.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20I%20booked%20an%20Airbnb%2C%20packed%20up%20my%20dogs%20and%20cat%2C%20and%20drove%20to%20Chicago%20to%20test%20out%20the%20city%20for%20a%20month.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%2C%20I%20flew%20back%20to%20Tennessee%20and%20listed%20my%20home%20for%20sale.%20I%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20furniture%20into%20storage%20and%20donated%20other%20items.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222397%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muller%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65203c876561dd877e734045%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuller%20in%20Chicago.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Channing%20Muller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20live%20in%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Chicago.%20My%20rent%20is%20%242%2C050%20a%20month.%20Quite%20frankly%2C%20I%20love%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20up%20responsibility.%20All%20I%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20are%20my%20pets%2C%20keeping%20my%20business%20running%2C%20and%20training%20for%20more%20marathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20realized%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20big%20home%20or%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20to%20be%20happy%