0of%20stairs%2C%20and%20I%20also%20don't%20mind%20that%20the%20laundry%20is%20shared%20in%20the%20basement.%20While%20those%20might%20be%20deal%20breakers%20for%20other%20people%2C%20it's%20not%20for%20me.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EReturning%20to%20renting%20has%20given%20me%20more%20peace%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Chattanooga%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20be%20growing%20into%20that%20home%2C%20and%20it%20turns%20out%20I%20actually%20grew%20out%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20homeowner%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20You%20have%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20garden%2C%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20plumbing%20and%20pest%20control.%20After%20doing%20all%20of%20that%20on%20my%20own%20for%20so%20long%2C%20I%20just%20got%20really%20tired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20me%2C%20the%20big%20benefit%20of%20being%20a%20renter%20is%20not%20having%20so%20much%20responsibility.%20I%20get%20to%20just%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20call%20somebody%20if%20something%20has%20gone%20wrong.%20I%20really%20get%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20business%2C%20making%20new%20friends%2C%20and%20training.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muller%20at%20a%20baseball%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65203ec39f7ca8b2bbdc1ada%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuller%20at%20a%20baseball%20game.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Channing%20Muller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20in%20housing%20size%20has%20had%20an%20effect%20on%20the%20dogs%20and%20it's%20affected%20my%20lifestyle.%20In%20Tennessee%2C%20I%20had%20a%20fence%20built%20around%20my%20backyard%20and%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20weather%20was%20like%2C%20I%20could%20open%20up%20my%20back%20door%20and%20they%20could%20go%20outside.%20Now%20I%20have%20to%20walk%20downstairs%20and%20take%20them%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20additional%20transition%20I%20noticed%20with%20downsizing%20is%20that%20I%20used%20to%20entertain%20a%20lot%20and%20have%20big%20dinner%20parties.%20Now%20I%20can%20have%20one%20or%20two%20friends%20over%20in%20my%20living%20room.%20I%20won't%20be%20doing%20dinner%20parties%20for%20a%20little%20while.%20It's%20a%20shift%20I%20think%20I%20will%20miss%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20holidays%20start%20to%20roll%20around.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Chicago%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65203f136e038039826bf3f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Chicago%20River.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Channing%20Muller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I%20will%20eventually%20become%20a%20homeowner%20again.%20I%20am%20a%20very%20big%20proponent%20of%20focusing%20on%20long-term%20wealth%20and%20long-term%20investments.%20I've%20owned%20a%20condo%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20I've%20owned%20a%20three-bedroom%20house%20in%20Chattanooga%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20those%20was%20an%20absolutely%20wonderful%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20just%20not%20ready%20for%20it%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20could%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownsizing-from-house-rental-apartment-upgrade-happiness-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696761181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65203fd16561dd877e734867%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownsizing-from-house-rental-apartment-upgrade-happiness-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Downsizing%20from%20a%20house%20to%20a%20rental%20apartment%20helped%20Channing%20Muller%20realize%20what%20makes%20her%20happy.%20She%20may%20choose%20homeownership%20again%20in%20the%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownsizing-from-house-rental-apartment-upgrade-happiness-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''This%20Is%20Our%209%2F11''%3A%20Israeli%20Envoy%20After%20Hamas'%20Surprise%20Attack%20On%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20has%20launched%20an%20unprecedented%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20with%20its%20fighters%20taking%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%20hostage.%C2%A0Over%20300%20Israelis%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20while%20the%20Palestinian%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20climbed%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%20232%20as%20a%20result%20of%20intense%20air%20strikes%20on%20the%20coastal%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECondemning%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20escalation%20and%20compared%20it%20with%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attack%20on%20the%20United%20States.%20In%20an%20interview%20on%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-ambassador-calls-hamas-attack-israel-truly-unprecedented-9-11%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BFox%20News%20Live%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20Saturday%2C%C2%A0Gilad%20Erdan%20called%20Hamas%20terrorists%20''animals''%20and%20condemned%20the%20military%20group%20for%20killing%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''Babies%2C%20women%2C%20and%20the%20elderly%20were%20dragged%20outside%20of%20their%20homes%2C%20were%20taken%20hostage.%20Civilians%20were%20shot%20and%20most%20were%20massacred%20in%20cold%20blood%20walking%20on%20the%20streets.%20This%20is%20something%20that%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20is%20truly%20unprecedented%2C''%20he%20told%20Fox%20News'%20Eric%20Shawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomat%20explained%20that%20because%20Israel's%20population%20is%20smaller%20than%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20casualties%