%3Cp%3EStella%20Kalinina%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAnzelika%20Akimova%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20Arina%2C%20left%20Ukraine%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20invasion%20and%20landed%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAkimova%20found%20her%20footing%20in%20a%20boxing%20gym%20run%20by%20a%20Russian%20trainer%20who%20became%20a%20grounding%20force.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHer%20story%20is%20a%20window%20into%20the%20challenges%20many%20Ukrainian%20refugees%20have%20faced%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20political%20support%20was%20on%20their%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20refugee%20named%20Anzelika%20Akimova%20enters%20her%20fighting%20stance%20at%20the%20Eastern%20Block%20Boxing%20gym%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20front%20of%20a%20neon%20logo%20of%20a%20screaming%20Eurasian%20brown%20bear%2C%20she's%20channeling%20a%20hypnotic%20rhythm%20that's%20interrupted%20only%20by%20booming%20drill%20instructions%20or%20the%20beep%20of%20a%20timer.%20The%20gym%20has%20the%20brutalist%20black-and-white%20aesthetic%20of%20a%20Russian%20nightclub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAkimova%2C%20her%20blue%20eyes%20laser-focused%2C%20cannons%20her%20left-handed%20jab%2C%20and%20a%20tattoo%20of%20angel%20wings%20sprawled%20across%20her%20back%20contracts%20and%20expands.%20She%20got%20the%20tattoo%20months%20after%20arriving%20in%20the%20US%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20both%20her%20name%2C%20rooted%20from%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bangel%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20new%20home%2C%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20across%20California%2C%20front%20yards%20don%20Ukrainian%20flags%20and%20cars%20are%20adorned%20with%20bumper%20stickers%20extending%20solidarity%20to%20the%20population%20under%20Russia's%20assault%2C%20which%20intensified%20after%20the%20country's%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%20February%202022%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.unh