Cfigcaption%3EA%20Hooptown%20Youth%20League%20game.%3Cp%3EChris%20Elam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nilson%20and%20others%20created%20HYL%2C%20they%20required%C2%A0players%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhooptownusa.com%2Fpages%2Ffaq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esign%20up%20individually%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20with%20a%20preorganized%20team%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20grouped%C2%A0them%20based%20on%20where%20they%20lived.%20Nilson%20said%20this%20eliminated%20the%20hurdle%20of%20establishing%20one's%20own%20team%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20allowed%20practices%20to%20be%20held%20near%20players'%20homes%2C%20and%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20super%20teams.%20Plus%2C%20the%20league%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20some%20local%20school%20superintendents%20to%20open%20up%20their%20gyms%20for%20free%20practices.%20This%20enabled%20the%20league%20to%20get%20the%20average%20cost%20for%20a%20single%20season%20down%20to%20roughly%20%24150%20per%20player%20or%20%2430%20for%20qualifying%20low-income%20families%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20to%20all%20of%20it%20is%20being%20able%20to%20get%20into%20our%20public-school%20gyms%20and%20be%20able%20to%20access%20them%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20league's%20efforts%20seem%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kxly.com%2Fnews%2Fhooptown-youth-league-is-helping-grow-basketball-in-spokane%2Farticle_50f30cf8-1449-11ee-9937-e727f9211315.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20thus%20far.%203%2C000%20kids%20from%20Spokane%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20participated%20in%20the%20league's%20first%20year%2C%20Nilson%20said%2C%20and%20over%203%2C800%20are%20registered%20to%20play%20this%20fall.%20The%20cost%20savings%20were%20particularly%20important%20for%20Curtin's%20family%20%E2%80%94%20she%20said%20her%20husband%20