nd%2C'%20but%20at%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%206.30%20a.m.%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Hamas%20fired%20a%20huge%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20into%20southern%20Israel.%20Air%20raid%20sirens%20across%20Israel%20shattered%20the%20morning%20silence%20and%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20air%20defence%20systems%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20again%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%2C000%20Rockets%20Rained%20From%20Sky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20launched%205%2C000%20rockets%20and%20in%20response%2C%20Israel's%20military%20fired%202%2C500%20rockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20said%20that%20smoke%20billowed%20over%20residential%20Israeli%20areas%20and%20people%20sheltered%20behind%20buildings%20as%20sirens%20were%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20announce%20the%20start%20of%20Operation%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%20and%20we%20announce%20that%20the%20first%20strike%2C%20which%20targeted%20enemy%20positions%2C%20airports%2C%20and%20military%20fortifications%2C%20exceeded%205%2C000%20missiles%20and%20shells%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20Deif%2C%20head%20of%20the%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20the%20military%20wing%20of%20Hamas%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20300%20Israelis%20and%20232%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20deadliest%20escalation%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael's%20reaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20face%20of%20evil.%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20criminal%20attack%2C%20without%20distinguishing%20between%20women%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly.%20It%20will%20realise%20very%20quickly%20that%20it%20made%20a%20grave%20mistake.%20We%20will%20change%20the%20face%20of%20reality%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20defence%20minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Iron%20Dome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Iron%20Dome%20missile%20defence%20system%20is%20a%20land-based%20air%20defence%20system.%20It%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20and%20destroy%20short-range%20rockets%2C%20mortars%2C%20and%20artillery%20shells%20fired%20from%20distances%20of%204%20kilometres%20to%2070%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20has%20guarded%20Israel%20since%202011.%20During%20the%202006%20Lebanon%20conflict%2C%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20were%20fired%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20several%20northern%20areas%20including%20Haifa%20were%20attacked%2C%20killing%20many.%20The%202006%20attacks%20prompted%20Israel%20to%20develop%20its%20own%20air%20defence%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%201987%20during%20the%20First%20Intifada%2C%20Hamas'%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20an%20Islamic%20state%20in%20Palestine.%20The%20group%20currently%20governs%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20territory%20on%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20coast.%20After%20winning%20the%202006%20Palestinian%20legislative%20elections%2C%20it%20seized%20control%20of%20Gaza%20in%202007%20following%20a%20violent%20conflict%20with%20its%20rival%2C%20Fatah.%20Since%20then%2C%20Hamas%20has%20been%20the%20de%20facto%20authority%20in%20Gaza%2C%20while%20Fatah%20governs%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20considered%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20Israel%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20Conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20began%20with%20Israel's%202005%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20In%20August%202005%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20unilaterally%20withdrew%20from%20Gaza%2038%20years%20after%20capturing%20it%20from%20Egypt%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20war%2C%20abandoning%20settlements%20and%20leaving%20the%20enclave%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202006%2C%20the%20Islamist%20group%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20seats%20in%20a%20Palestinian%20legislative%20election.%20Israel%20and%20the%20U.S.%20cut%20off%20aid%20to%20Palestinians%20because%20Hamas%20refuses%20to%20renounce%20violence%20and%20recognise%20Israel%2C%20the%20international%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20conflict%20was%20not%20resolved%20and%20in%20Jan%202023%20Islamic%20Jihad%20in%20Gaza%20fired%20two%20rockets%20towards%20Israel%20after%20Israeli%20troops%20raided%20a%20refugee%20camp%20and%20killed%20seven%20Palestinian%20gunmen%20and%20two%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20the%20biggest%20attack%20on%20Israel%20in%20years%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20was%20on%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20adding%20it%20had%20carried%20out%20strikes%20targeting%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20had%20called%20up%20reservists.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696758120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F3co5q298_israel-palestine-reuters-_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-happened-in-israel-all-about-israel-palestine-conflict-in-gaza-4461443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20300%20Israelis%20and%20232%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20deadliest%20escalation%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20in%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-happened-in-israel-all-about-israel-palestine-conflict-in-gaza-4461443%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-happened-in-israel