-2024-is-rfk-jr-going-to-ditch-the-democratic-party-and-run-as-an-independent%2Famp_articleshow%2F104258749.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-election-2024-is-rfk-jr-going-to-ditch-the-democratic-party-and-run-as-an-independent%2Famp_articleshow%2F104258749.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20thought%20I%20landed%20my%20dream%20job%20at%20Amazon.%20But%20after%20being%20put%20on%20an%20impossible%20performance%20plan%2C%20I%20quit%20even%20though%20I%20lost%20a%20%24110%2C000%20deposit%20on%20a%20house.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20walks%20on%20the%20street%20near%20the%20Amazon%20headquarters%20in%20Seattle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6520574a9f7ca8b2bbdc599b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon%20has%20a%20performance-review%20system%20that%20includes%20an%20improvement%20program%20called%20Pivot.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Ryder%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20Amazon%20employee%20said%20he%20quit%20after%20being%20put%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-annual-performance-review-process-bonus-salary-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPivot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20performance-improvement%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeing%20out%20of%20work%20meant%20he%20lost%20the%20deposit%20on%20a%20house%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20building.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20performance-improvement%20plan%20is%20only%20used%20to%20address%20work%20output%2C%20an%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20former%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20employee.%20Though%20he%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20his%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Insider.%20The%20employee%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-does-amazon-performance-improvement-plan-work-focus-pivot-fired-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecompany's%20Pivot%20program%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20performance-improvement%20plan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20in%20tech%20when%20an%20Amazon%20recruiter%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20on%20LinkedIn.%20I'm%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20so%20Amazon%2C%20AWS%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that's%20it%2C%20right%3F%20That's%20the%20company%20you%20want%20to%20go%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20going%20to%20really%20take%20me%20to%20that%20next%20level%20and%20lead%20me%20to%20my%20dream%20job.%20After%20I%20get%20the%20job%2C%20I%20think%20things%20are%20going%20really%20well.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20sell%20our%20house%2C%20take%20the%20money%2C%20and%20use%20it%20to%20build%20a%20bigger%20house%20because%20we%20have%20a%20large%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20months%20to%20design%20it%20and%20get%20construction%20going.%20But%20then%20things%20began%20to%20change%20at%20work.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I'm%20getting%20stressed.%20It%20felt%20like%20what%20they%20were%20asking%20me%20to%20do%20was%20a%20moving%20target%20and%20I%20could%20never%20hit%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20would%20be%20pushed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20it%20happened%2C%20I%20was%20shocked.%20And%20my%20wife%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20the%20house%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20tough%20interview%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20all%20started%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20about%20joining%20Amazon.%20The%20recruiter%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20and%20I%20interviewed%20with%20him.%20It%20was%20a%20tough%20process.%20There%20were%20three%20or%20four%20different%20rounds.%20Then%20they%20gave%20me%20an%20offer%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20great.%20And%20then%20they%20said%20they%20were%20going%20to%20give%20me%20a%20signing%20bonus.%20The%20recruiter%20said%20that%20it%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20in%20terms%20of%20pay%20and%20advancement.%20So%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWow%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20work%20for%20Amazon.%20And%20that's%20just%20the%20beginning.%20And%20I'm%20making%20this%20much.%20I'm%20set.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20start%20and%20everything%20seems%20fine.%20I%20met%20my%20manager.%20And%20he%20seemed%20pretty%20nice.%20I%20mean%2C%20you%20know%2C%20normal%20IT%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20excitement%20when%20I%20started%20there%20because%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20people.%20It%20was%20pretty%20good%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20off%20the%20bat%20is%20three%20months%20where%20you%20do%20all%20the%20training.%20They%20teach%20you%20about%20the%20cloud.%20They%20prepare%20you%20to%20be%20a%20technical%20account%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20a%20TAM.%20And%20it's%20just%20three%20months%2C%20which%20is%20really%20stressful.%20You%20prepare%20presentations%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20talk%20to%20customers.%20They%20call%20that%20process%20the%20check%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20gonna%20give%20you%20more%20shares%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20check%20ride%20into%20the%20actual%20job%20is%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20terrible.%20They%20don't%20tell%20you%20anything%20about%20how%20to%20do%20your%20job.%20And%20I%20talked%20with%20other%20new%20TAMs%20and%20they%20felt%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20that%2C%20a%20few%20more%20TAMs%20joined%20my%20team.%20I%20was%20becoming%20a%20bit%20more%20of%20a%20senior%20TAM%20in%20my%20role.%20There%20are%20opportunities%20that%20you%20have%20there%20to%20be%20what%20they%20call%20an%20onboarding%20buddy.%20When%20there's%20somebody%20new%20you%20become%20a%20mentor%20for%20them.%20So%20I%20did%20that%20on%20top%20of%20my%20job%2C%20and%20I%20did%20a%20pretty%20good%20job.%20And%20people%20started%20to%20get%20to%20know%20me%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOK%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20him.%20He%20can%20be%20a%20coach%20for%20you%20to%20help%20you%20with%20check%20ride.%26quot%3B%20By%20then%20I'm%20like%20only%20four%20months%20into%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20have%20one-on-ones%20with%20my%20manager%2C%20which%20were%20very%2C%20very%20simple.%20It%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20how's%20it%20going%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20I'd%20say%20it%20was%20going%20well%20and%20that%20I%20was%20still%20learning%20my%20customers.%20And%20then%2C%20one%20time%20in%20a%20one-on-one%2C%20my%20manager%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20the%20VPs%20look%20at%20performance%20and%20this%20and%20that%2C%20and%20we're%20gonna%20give%20you%20more%20shares.%26quot%3B%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20awesome.%20Just%20months%20into%20the%20job%20and%20I'm%20getting%20extra%20Amazon%20stock.%20My%20manager%20said%20not%20everyone%20was%20getting%20more%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sudden%20shift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I%20look%20back%2C%20soon%20after%20I%20started%20working%20on%20a%20processing%20a%20big%20refund%20for%20a%20customer%20who'd%20been%20overbilled%20was%20when%20my%20manager%20met%20with%20me%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20my%20performance.%20It%20threw%20me%20off.%20%26quot%3BManagement%20doesn't%20really%20see%20what%20you're%20doing%20and%20this%20and%20this.%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWait%20a%20minute%2C%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20you%20gave%20me%20more%20shares.%20Everything%20was%20fine.%20And%20now%20this.%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20for%20my%20customer.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20going%20to%20meet%20with%20me%20every%20week%20and%20give%20me%20assignments.%20I%20didn't%20know%20who%20to%20talk%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20would%20say%20things%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHave%20you%20read%20this%20document%20on%20TAM%20expectations%3F%26quot%3