2C%20and%20connections.%20For%20many%20of%20them%2C%20I%20had%20no%20other%20contact%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeeks%20passed%20as%20I%20persisted%20but%20nothing%20happened.%20My%20angst%20escalated%20from%20panic%20to%20visceral%20anxiety.%20Constant%20knots%20in%20my%20stomach%20and%20neck%20fought%20for%20my%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20I%20could%20think%20about%20was%20how%20to%20fix%20this%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20I'd%20been%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20world%20both%20mentally%20and%20emotionally.%20It%20would%20have%20felt%20empowering%20to%20decide%20to%20take%20a%20detox%20break%20from%20social%20media.%20Having%20it%20forced%20upon%20me%20was%20discombobulating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20morning%2C%20I%20woke%20with%20a%20sudden%20jolt%20of%20reality.%20I%20might%20never%20get%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20at%20Facebook%20to%20see%20that%20they'd%20issued%20an%20unwarranted%20shut%20down%20of%20my%20account.%20This%20compelled%20me%20to%20look%20at%20the%20situation%20in%20a%20new%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20banned%20gave%20me%20clarity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20truth%20of%20my%20Facebook%20habits.%20I'd%20been%20posting%20and%20checking%20notifications%20several%20times%20daily%20for%20years.%20My%20brain%20babbled%20in%20the%20background%20about%20other%20people's%20posts%20and%20how%20I'd%20frame%20my%20own.%20That%20incessant%20mind%20chatter%20never%20shut%20down%2C%20even%20when%20the%20app%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20like%20working%20with%20a%20super%20slow%20computer%20where%20the%20frustration%20mounts%20and%20you're%20ready%20to%20throw%20it%20through%20a%20window.%20Then%20you%20finally%20realize%20there's%20a%20dozen%20apps%20running%20in%20the%20background%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20it's%20bogged%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20forced%20shutdown%20was%20a%20reboot%2C%20providing%20much%20needed%20calm%20and%20clarity.%20The%20disconnection%20from%20Facebook%20taught%20me%20some%20key%20lessons.%20Looking%20back%20on%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20I%20can%20see%20how%20the%20changes%20to%20my%20social%20media%20habits%20are%20improving%20my%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBrief%20one%20or%20two%20day%20social%20media%20breaks%20aren't%20enough%20to%20clear%20my%20head.%20I'd%20done%20those%20digital%20detoxes%20before.%20I%20never%20felt%20completely%20free%20of%20the%20incessant%20mental%20chatter.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20took%20me%20about%20two%20weeks%20to%20feel%20better%20being%20off%20Facebook.%20On%20reflection%2C%20it's%20clear%20I%20could%20have%20experienced%20mental%20calm%20sooner%20if%20I%20hadn't%20dwelled%20on%20my%20lack%20of%20control%20over%20the%20situation.%20I%20think%20a%20seven%20day%20detox%20from%20my%20other%20social%20accounts%20is%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20me%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EDeep%2C%20meaningful%20connection%20boosts%20my%20happiness.%20Being%20banned%20forced%20me%20to%20consider%20the%20quality%20of%20my%20relationships.%20I%20asked%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20of%20these%20people%20would%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20if%20I%20had%20to%20make%20the%20effort%20of%20only%20connecting%20one%20on%20one%3F%26quot%3B%20There's%20a%20bigger%20time%20and%20energy%20investment%20required%20for%20individual%20messages%20vs.%20Facebook%20blasts.%20Acknowledging%20this%20reminded%20me%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20stay%20intentional%20about%20connecting.%20I%20started%20taking%20the%20necessary%20steps%20to%20maintain%20relationships%20with%20those%20who%20matter%20most%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EI%20function%20best%20when%20I%20align%20my%20life%20with%20my%20strengths.%20Being%20banned%20from%20Facebook%20helped%20me%20see%20that%20a%20platform%20built%20for%20scrolling%20isn't%20where%20I'm%20meant%20to%20be.%20My%20superpower%20is%20writing%20nuanced%20long-form%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20felt%20panicked%20and%20powerless%20over%20Facebook%20banning%20my%20account.%20Today%2C%20I'm%20grateful%20for%20the%20experience.%20It%20gifted%20me%20a%20fresh%20perspective.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20has%20made%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20my%20business%2C%20relationships%2C%20and%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbanned-from-facebook-account-suspended-improved-mental-health-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696756621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651db85f42ecf94db4781c0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbanned-from-facebook-account-suspended-improved-mental-health-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20banned%20from%20Facebook%20and%20don't%20miss%20it.%20I'm%20glad%20my%20account%20was%20suspended%20because%20it%20showed%20me%20how%20bad%20social%20media%20was%20for%20my%20mental%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Leah%20Borski)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbanned-from-facebook-account-suspended-improved-mental-health-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22International%20Sales%20Agents%20Discuss%20Popularity%20of%20Asian%20LGBT%2C%20Horror%20Genres%2C%20%E2%80%98Love-Hate%E2%80%99%20Relationship%20With%20Netflix%20at%20Busan%20ACFM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696756607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBusan-Sales-Agents.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235748434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20enduring%20popularity%20of%20the%20Asian%20LGBT%20and%20horror%20genres%20and%20the%20relationshi