mp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fjoyalukkas-to-open-40-new-showrooms-in-india-abroad-in-next-2-years-123100800364_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20spotted%20more%20fake%20Rolexes%20than%20I%20can%20count%20in%20my%20career%20as%20a%20professional%20watch%20dealer%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20how%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221260%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fake%20Rolexes%20are%20no%20match%20for%20watch%20expert%20John%20Buckley%2C%20shown%20here%20on%20the%20job%20in%20black%20shirt%20and%20hat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65206f1f6561dd877e73b7f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFake%20Rolex%20vs.%20real%3A%20NYC%20watch%20dealerJohn%20Buckley%20knows%20exactly%20how%20to%20spot%20a%20fake%20Rolex%20after%20working%20with%20luxury%20watches%20for%2026%20years.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohn%20Buckley%20is%20a%20watch%20dealer%20with%2026%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERolexes%20are%20his%20specialty%2C%20and%20he%20said%20fake%20ones%20just%20jump%20out%20him%20because%20of%20a%20few%20telltale%20signs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20the%20most%20important%20things%20to%20look%20at%20when%20gauging%20authenticity%20are%20the%20dial%20and%20the%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20John%20Buckley%2C%20a%2059-year-old%20watch%20dealer%20with%20offices%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20New%20Jersey%20who's%20the%20owner%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftuscanyrose.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ETuscanyRose%20LLC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvookum.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EVookum%20Media%20Group%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20loved%20watches.%20I%20began%20dealing%20in%20the%20NYC%20Diamond%20District%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20mostly%20buying%20and%20selling%20watches%20and%20watch%20parts.%20I%20specialize%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-models-worth-more-pre-owned-used-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evintage%20and%20modern%20Rolex%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20while%20I%20have%20experience%20in%20all%20luxury%20brands%2C%20Rolex%20is%20my%20forte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20out%20selling%20from%20watch%20catalogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20go%20to%20Tourneau%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Rolex-authorized%20dealer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20a%20couple%20of%20different%20watch%20catalogs%20and%20sell%20from%20them.%20It%20felt%20like%20free%20money.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20save%20enough%20for%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20my%20first%20house%20in%20New%20Jersey%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20began%20specializing%20in%20watch%20parts%3A%20cases%2C%20dials%2C%20hands%2C%20and%20bracelets.%20I%20looked%20at%20it%20like%20a%20chop%20shop%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20need%20a%20fender%20for%20your%20car%20and%20somebody's%20got%20it%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20pay%20whatever%20you%20have%20to%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20by%20going%20booth%20to%20booth%20on%2047th%20Street%2C%20and%20if%20you%20found%20a%20part%20that%20was%20worth%20two%20to%20three%20times%20what%20you%20could%20buy%20it%20for%2C%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20deal.%20You%20could%20also%20post%20stuff%20online%20in%20chat%20rooms%20or%20on%20eBay%2C%20and%20you%20could%20make%20money%20while%20you%20were%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20money%20I%20made%20selling%20from%20catalogs%20and%20grew%20from%20there%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20we're%20a%20family-owned%2C%20self-funded%20small%20business.%20We%20have%20no%20affiliation%20with%20any%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hate%20when%20people%20throw%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bexpert%26quot%3B%20around%20when%20they've%20been%20in%20the%20watch%20business%20two%20or%20three%20years.%20After%2026%20years%2C%20when%20I'm%20looking%20at%20fake%20watches%2C%20they%20jump%20out%20at%20me.%20I%20can%20literally%20put%20a%20watch%20in%20my%20hand%20and%20just%20know%20that%20something%20isn't%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20crazy%20business%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20egos%20in%20it%2C%20and%20mine%20is%20probably%20right%20up%20there%20with%20everybody%20else's.%20The%20sense%20of%20entitlement%20I%20carry%20with%20me%20is%20because%20I've%20made%20mistakes%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20them%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20spotted%20more%20fakes%20in%20my%20career%20than%20I%20can%20count%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20ask%20me%20how%20someone%20can%20bring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-watches-luxury-market-replica-ceo-omega-dealer-demand-swiss-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efake%20Rolex%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20store%20and%20the%20store%20doesn't%20catch%20it.%20Sometimes%20it's%20a%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20you%20would%20think%20the%20store%20clerks%20would%20know%20this%20stuff%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20cases%20where%20someone%20really%20took%20the%20time%20to%20try%20to%20fool%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20I%20call%20those%20the%20dangerous%20fakes.%20We%20get%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20vintage%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22636%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20spot%20a%20fake%20Rolex%2C%20shown%20side%20by%20side%20with%20a%20real%20Rolex%20in%20a%20person's%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6520715d6561dd877e73bc73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22790%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuckley%20compares%20a%20real%20Rolex%20Daytona%20watch%20with%20a%20fake%20in%20a%20TikTok%20video.%3Cp%3ETikTok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20watches%20shipped%20to%20me%20from%20private%20people.%20I'll%20look%20at%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20obviously%20fake%2C%20so%20you've%20got%20to%20break%20somebody's%20heart%20or%20just%20call%20them%20out.%20It%20doesn't%20happen%20often%2C%20but%20we%20handle%20a%20minimum%20of%20100-200%20pieces%20a%20month%2C%20and%20I%20get%20about%20one%20fake%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20looked%20at%20a%20watch%20from%20a%20seller%20who's%20very%20popular%20online.%20Many%20buyers%20see%20a%20seller%20online%20who's%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20followers%20and%20they%20assume%20credibility.%20That's%20a%20bad%20call%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20these%20sellers%20are%20basically%20salespeople%20with%20no%20skin%20in%20the%20game.%20You%20can't%20trust%20them%20on%20a%20watch%20that%20you're%20spending%20%2410%2C000-plus%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%205%20things%20I%20look%20for%20when%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ft%2FZT8MWMAaD%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eidentify%20a%20fake%20Rolex%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Mechanics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20look%20at%20are%20the%20screws%20on%20the%20bracelet%20or%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20watch.%20On%20a%20counterfeit%2C%20the%20screw%20heads%20and%20bracelet%20fittings%20aren't%20as%20crisp%20as%20they%20would%20be%20on%20authentic%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20problem%20if%20the%20screws%20don't%20go%20down%20flush%20on%20the%20back%20side%2C%20and%20you%20can%20see%20if%20screw%20heads%20aren't%20flush%20on%20top.%20Because%20the%20counterfeit%20companies%20don't%20pay%20attention%20to%20detail%2C%20that's%20a%20big%20red%20flag%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Case%20symmetry%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20back%20of%20a%20modern%20Rolex%20watch%2C%20where%20the%20bracelet%20meets%20the%20case%20(which%20holds%20the%20movement%2C%20or%20engine%2C%20of%20the%20watch%20and%20has%20the%20serial%20numbering)%2C%20a%20real%20Rolex%20is%20going%20to%20fit%20perfectly%20like%20a%20glove%20and%20slip%20in%20there%20with%20no%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20lot%20of%20counterfeit%20watches%2C%20you'll%20notice%20small%20very%20gaps%20all%20the%20way%20around.%20The%20metal%20isn't%20finished%20properly%2C%20and%20it%20just%20doesn't%20look%20crisp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Dial%2Fface%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dial%20of%20a%20watch%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%20to%20really%20understand%20and%20the%20hardest%20to%20spot%20to%20examine%20for%20the%20untrained%20eye.%20Font%20details%2C%20text%20placement%2C%20and%20luminous%20material%20are%20all%20telltale%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20some%20of%20the%20new%20counterfeit%20watches%2C%20the%20makers%20try%20to%20master%20this%20stuff%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20always%20something%20that%20will%20be%20a%20giveaway.%20If%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20watch%20that's%2050%20years%20old%20and%20the%20case%20has%20wear%20on%20it%20but%20the%20face%20looks%20like%20it%20was%20made%20yesterday%2C%20chances%20are%20something's%20not%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Movement%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tell-tale%20mechanical%20sign%20is%20when%20the%20%26quot%3Bcloned%26quot%3B%20movements%20(the%20engines%20that%20make%20the%20watches%20run)%20are%20close%20but%20not%20passable%20in%20terms%20of%20millwork%2C%20finishing%2C%20etc.%20If%20you%20Google%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FRepTime%2Fcomments%2Fwxu9vm%2Fbeginners_guide_to_the_clone_movements_found_in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecloned%20Rolex%20movements%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20new%20hairspring%20%E2%80%94%20the%20main%20spring%20in%20the%20balance%20wheel%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20newer%20Rolexes%20have%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20crappier%20cloned%20movements%20don't%20have%20that.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20finishes%2C%20the%20counterfeits%20aren't%20crisp%20or%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Pricing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20spot%20something%20amiss%20is%20by%20pricing.%20If%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20watch%20with%20a%20normal%20market%20value%20of%20%2414%2C000%20to%20%2415%2C000%20and%20someone%20is%20trying%20to%20sell%20it%20for%20%248%2C000%20or%20%249%2C000%2C%20there's%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%20there's%20a%20story%20attached%20to%20it%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BI%20won%20it%20in%20a%20card%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BA%20friend%20at%20the%20office%20sold%20it%20to%20me%3B%20he%20needed%20money.%26quot%3B%20My%20favorite%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20grandmother%20had%20it%20in%20her%20sock%20drawer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20these%20new%20counterfeits%20that%20pop%20up%20come%20with%20Rolex%20cards%20that%20have%20numbers%20on%20them%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20if%20you%20handle%20the%20real%20cards%20every%20day%2C%20you'll%20spot%20immediately.%20A%20novice%20will%20never%20know%20the%20difference%2C%20but%20usually%20the%20price%20point%20gives%20it%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperience%20is%20everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20parts%20business%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fluxury-watch-economy-markets-recession-patek-swiss-subdial-index-rolex-2023-6%3F_gl%3D1*1ub094b*_ga*MjE0NjY1MzcwOC4xNjU3OTAyMzQ0*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5NjYyNDUwMy4xMjUzLjEuMTY5NjYyNDY0MS41Ny4wLjA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20watch%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20really%20catapulted%20my%20ability%20to%20identify%20whether%20or%20not%20a%20watch%20was%20real%20or%20fake.%20Buyers%2C%2