ign%20that%20featured%20the%20Union%20Jack%20and%20the%20RIAF%20roundel%20(red%2C%20white%20and%20blue).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20start%20a%20new%20chapter%20in%20the%20history%20of%20IAF%2C%20let%20us%20all%20strive%20to%20be%20the%20change%20that%20we%20want%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Chaudhari%20said%20in%20his%20Air%20Force%20Day%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20us%20work%20together%20to%20take%20our%20air%20force%20to%20greater%20heights%20and%20let%20us%20use%20our%20commitment%20and%20collective%20capacity%20to%20achieve%20excellence%20in%20all%20that%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20was%20officially%20established%20on%208%20October%2C%201932.%20In%20view%20of%20its%20professional%20efficiency%20and%20achievements%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20force%20was%20bestowed%20with%20the%20prefix%20%26quot%3BRoyal%26quot%3B%20in%20March%201945.%20So%2C%20it%20became%20the%20Royal%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(RIAF).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201950%2C%20the%20IAF%20dropped%20its%20%26quot%3BRoyal%26quot%3B%20prefix%20and%20amended%20the%20ensign%20as%20India%20became%20a%20Republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RIAF%20ensign%20consisted%20of%20the%20Union%20Jack%20in%20the%20upper%20left%20canton%20and%20the%20RIAF%20roundel%20(red%2C%20white%20and%20blue)%20on%20the%20fly%20side.%20Post-Independence%2C%20the%20IAF%20ensign%20was%20created%20by%20replacing%20the%20Union%20Jack%20with%20the%20Indian%20tricolour%20and%20the%20RAF%20roundels%20with%20the%20IAF%20tricolour%20roundel%20in%20the%20lower%20right%20canton.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20new%20lAF%20ensign%20has%20now%20been%20created%20to%20better%20reflect%20the%20values%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20This%20reaffirmation%20will%20now%20be%20reflected%20by%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%20Crest%20in%20the%20top%20right%20corner%20of%20the%20ensign%2C%20towards%20the%20fly%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IAF%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20crest%20has%20the%20national%20symbol%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20lion%20on%20the%20top%20with%20the%20words%20'Satyameva%20Jayate'%20in%20Devanagari%20below%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBelow%20the%20Ashoka%20lion%20is%20a%20Himalayan%20eagle%20with%20its%20wings%20spread%2C%20denoting%20the%20fighting%20qualities%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20ring%20in%20light%20blue%20colour%20encircles%20the%20Himalayan%20eagle%20with%20the%20words%20'Bhartiya%20Vayu%20Sena'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20motto%20of%20the%20IAF%20--%20'touch%20the%20sky%20with%20the%20glory'%20is%20inscribed%20below%20Himalayan%20eagle%20in%20Devanagari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IAF%20motto%20has%20been%20taken%20from%20verse%2024%2C%20Chapter%2011%20of%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20and%20means%20%26quot%3BRadiant%20Thou%20Touchest%20Heaven%26quot%3B%20or%20in%20other%20words%20%26quot%3Btouching%20the%20sky%20with%20glory%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20Day%20parade%20was%20held%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20was%20traditionally%20held%20at%20the%20Hindon%20airbase%20near%20Delhi%20till%202021%20before%20the%20event%20was%20taken%20outside%20the%20national%20capital.%20It%20was%20held%20in%20Chandigarh%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696752120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0a0v6cu8_air-chief-unveils-new-insignia_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-chief-vr-chaudhari-unveils-new-ensign-at-air-force-day-parade-in-prayagraj-4461121%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20of%20Air%20Staff%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20VR%20Chaudhari%20on%20Sunday%20unveiled%20a%20new%20ensign%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20