0for%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Soma%20Ravi%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%20working%20in%20Israel%20for%2018%20years%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-hamas-rocket-attack-what-we-know-about-hamas-group-behind-terror-attack-on-israel-4460980%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20What%20Hamas%20Wants%2C%20And%20Who%20Backs%20Its%20Fight%20Against%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20declared%20a%20'state%20of%20war'%20and%20launched%20an%20offensive%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20group%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20sensitive%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFearing%20the%20war%2C%20Vikas%20Sharma%2C%20an%20Indian%20student%20at%20the%20Hebrew%20University%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20tense%20situation%20in%20Israel%20because%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20but%20all%20the%20Indian%20students%20are%20safe.%20Most%20of%20the%20students%20are%20staying%20in%20dorms%20and%20accommodations%20provided%20by%20the%20college.%20We%20are%20in%20contact%20with%20each%20other%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20through%20WhatsApp.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20night%2C%20the%20Representative%20Office%20of%20India%20in%20Ramallah%20posted%20a%20public%20notice%20urging%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20Palestine%20to%20contact%20the%20office%20in%20case%20of%20emergency.%20The%20notice%20provided%20two%20contact%20numbers%20for%20a%2024%2F7%20emergency%20helpline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bloodiest%20escalation%20of%20the%20conflict%20since%20the%201973%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20massive%20rocket%20barrage%20and%20ground%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20offensive%2C%20killing%20more%20than%20300%20Israelis%20and%20wounding%201%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Israeli%20ar