%20formidable%20aerial%20defence%20system%2C%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%20More%20than%20500%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Hamas'%20attack%20and%20Israel's%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20look%20at%20Hamas'%20history%2C%20ideology%20and%20demands%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Hamas%20Began%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20was%20founded%20in%201987%20by%20Ahmed%20Yassin%20and%20Abdel%20Aziz%20al-Rantissi%20as%20an%20arm%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20Muslim%20Brotherhood.%20Hamas%20stands%20for%20Harakat%20al-Muqawamah%20al-Islamiyya%2C%20meaning%20Islamic%20Resistance%20Movement.%20'Hamas'%20means%20zeal.%20In%201988%2C%20a%20Hamas%20Charter%20spelt%20out%20that%20its%20goal%20was%20to%20liberate%20Palestine%20and%20to%20establish%20an%20Islamic%20State%20in%20the%20area%20that%20spans%20Israel%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20In%20later%20years%2C%20the%20group%20has%20said%20it%20would%20accept%20a%20truce%20if%20Israel%20retreats%20to%20pre-1967%20borders%2C%20pays%20reparations%20and%20allows%20Palestinian%20refugees%20to%20return.%20It%20has%20also%20said%20it%20would%20end%20its%20links%20with%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood.%20Israel%2C%20however%2C%20has%20trashed%20Hamas'%20claims%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bfool%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%3A%20Structure%20And%20Support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20a%20cultural%20wing%2C%20Dawah%2C%20and%20a%20military%20arm%2C%20Izz%20ad-Din%20al-Qassam%20Brigades.%20Hamas%20enjoys%20the%20backing%20of%20Iran%20and%20is%20part%20of%20a%20bloc%20comprising%20Iran%2C%20Syria%20and%20Islamist%20group%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon.%20All%20the%20members%20of%20the%20bloc%20oppose%20the%20US%20policy%20in%20the%20region.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Iran's%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20said%20Hamas'%20attacks%20yesterday%20were%20proof%20of%20%26quot%3BPalestinian%20people's%20confidence%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20occupiers%26quot%3B.%20Hamas%20has%20supporters%20across%20Palestine%20territories%20and%20in%20other%20countries%20of%20the%20Middle%20East.%20In%20the%20region%2C%20Iran%2C%20Syria%20and%20Yemen%20have%20backed%20Hamas%20on%20the%20attacks%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bproud%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bheroic%26quot%3B.%20Qatar%20has%20held%20Israel%20solely%20responsible%20for%20the%20situation.%20Arab%20League%20and%20Jordan%2C%20too%2C%20have%20flagged%20Israel's%20policies%20and%20its%20link%20to%20the%20current%20conflict.%20Egypt%2C%20Morocco%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20have%20called%20for%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20Hamas%20has%20been%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Canada%2C%20Egypt%20and%20Japan.%20In%202018%2C%20a%20resolution%20moved%20by%20US%20to%20condemn%20Hamas'%20activities%20was%20voted%20down%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%20vs%20Fatah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas'%20emergence%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20political%20scene%20brought%20it%20in%20direct%20confrontation%20with%20Fatah%2C%20founded%20and%20led%20by%20Yasser%20Arafat.%20Founded%20as%20a%20paramilitary%20organisation%2C%20Fatah%2C%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20later%20gave%20up%20armed%20resistance%20and%20backed%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolution%20to%20build%20a%20Palestinian%20State%20as%20per%20the%201967%20borders%20alongside%20an%20Israeli%20State.%20Arafat's%20death%20in%202004%20created%20a%20vacuum%20amid%20which%20Hamas%20emerged%20stronger.%20In%202007%2C%20the%20group%20seized%20control%20in%20Gaza%20after%20a%20civil%20war%20with%20Fatah.%20Since%20then%2C%20Hamas%20has%20controlled%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20while%20Fatah%20holds%20power%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20While%20Hamas%20identifies%20itself%20as%20Islamist%2C%20Fatah%20advocates%20secularism.%20The%20two%20sides%20are%20also%20different%20in%20their%20approach%20towards%20Israel.%20Hamas%20does%20not%20recognise%20Israel.%20While%20Hamas%20calls%20for%20armed%20resistance%2C%20Fatah%20has%20pushed%20for%20negotiations%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out.%20The%20two%20forces%20have%20consistently%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20turf%20war%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20decades.%20Multiple%20agreements%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict%20have%20collapsed.%20The%20latest%20fallout%20of%20this%20conflict%20was%20Hamas%20boycotting%20the%202021-22%20Palestinian%20local%20elections.%20Fatah%20is%20currently%20led%20by%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%2C%20the%20President%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20after%20yesterday's%20attacks%2C%20the%20State%20of%20Palestine%20did%20not%20name%20Hamas%20and%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20warned%20against%20the%20consequences%20of%20blocking%20the%20political%20horizon%20and%20failing%20to%20enable%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20exercise%20their%20legitimate%20right%20to%20self-determination%20and%20establish%20long%20their%20own%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696750920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fofkvbmc_hamas-_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-hamas-rocket-attack-what-we-know-about-hamas-group-behind-terror-attack-on-israel-4460980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palestinian%20terrorist%20group%20Hamas%20made%20global%20headlines%20yesterday%20by%20firing%20over%205%2C000%20rockets%20at%20Israel%20and%20overpowering%20its%20formidable%20aerial%20defence%20system%2C%20the%20Iron%20Dome%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-hamas-rocket-attack-what-we-know-about-hamas-group-behind-terror-attack-on-israel-4460980%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org