y-2-hamas-lebanon-hezbollah-latest-updates%2Farticleshow%2F104255048.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDollars%20That%20Helped%20Fund%20Hamas%20Attack%20Came...%26quot%3B%3A%20Donald%20Trump's%20Big%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20President%20has%20accused%20his%20successor%20Joe%20Biden%20of%20%26quot%3Bindirectly%26quot%3B%20funding%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20Hamas%20attacks%20are%20a%20disgrace%20and%20Israel%20has%20every%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%20with%20overwhelming%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSadly%2C%20American%20taxpayer%20dollars%20helped%20fund%20these%20attacks%2C%20which%20many%20reports%20are%20saying%20came%20from%20the%20Biden%20Administration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump's%20allegations%20back%20Republican%20claims%20that%20%246%20billion%20released%20last%20month%20to%20Iran%20as%20part%20of%20a%20prisoner%20exchange%20deal%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20Deputy%20Press%20Secretary%20Andrew%20Bates%20said%20on%20social%20media%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20shameful%20lie%20in%20every%20respect%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20both%20parties%20should%20be%20totally%20united%20in%20supporting%20Israel's%20defense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20%26quot%3Bcan%20only%20be%20used%20for%20verifiable%20purchases%20of%20humanitarian%20needs%20like%20food%20and%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20added%2C%20in%20a%20fierce%20retort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20seemed%20little%20chance%20of%20keeping%20US%20partisan%20politics%20out%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20with%20the%20senior%20administration%20official%20saying%20that%20the%20situation%20in%20Congress%20-%20where%20the%20lower%20chamber%20currently%20lacks%20a%20leader%20-%20will%20likely%20complicate%20any%20US%20action.%3