ies.%20Patients%20who%20received%20the%20treatment%20early%20in%20life%20also%20showed%20the%20ability%20to%20even%20sit%20independently%20later%20in%20life.%20Since%20such%20treatments%20only%20help%20in%20preventing%20the%20condition%20from%20progressing%2C%20those%20who%20receive%20them%20require%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20support%20in%20the%20form%20of%20physiotherapy%2C%20which%20also%20adds%20to%20the%20costs%20of%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20exorbitant%20costs%20which%20make%20seeking%20treatment%20inaccessible%2C%20children%20with%20SMA%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20survival%20and%20often%20end%20up%20not%20making%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20continues.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20strong%20financial%20support%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20enhancing%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20886px)%20100vw%2C%20886px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Given%20how%C2%A0people%20with%20SMA%20often%20rely%20on%20mobility%20aids%2C%20an%20educational%20institution%20or%20workplace%20without%20proper%20access%20to%20different%20areas%20can%20mean%20limited%20learning%20as%20well%20as%20labour%20force%20participation.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129.jpg%20886w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129-300x195.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129-500x326.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_1835818411_11zon-1696514129-768x500.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co