ld%2C%20the%20setting%20is%20much%20more%20formal%20and%20clinical.%20To%20provide%20this%20comforting%20space%2C%20where%20one%20can%20express%20themselves%2C%20not%20just%20through%20words%2C%20but%20also%20through%20art%2C%20Pooja%20set%20up%20%E2%80%98The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%E2%80%99%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20wellness%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20we%20offer%20multiple%20services.%20We%20have%20counselling%20sessions%20for%20individuals%2C%20couples%2C%20families%2C%20and%20children.%20We%20have%20support%20groups%2C%20wellness%20workshops%20(where%20we%20use%20art%2C%20dance%20and%20drama%20to%20provide%20help)%20and%20group%20therapy%20sessions.%20We%20have%20designed%20our%20space%20to%20be%20one%20where%20people%20feel%20like%20opening%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98mental%20health%20cafe%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20founder%20likes%20to%20call%20it%2C%20is%20in%20T%20Nagar%2C%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20have%20a%20programme%20for%20children%20called%20Emotional%20Intelligence%20Through%20Arts%20(EITA).%20The%20focus%20is%20to%20nurture%20emotional%20intelligence%20in%20children%20by%20helping%20them%20express%20themselves%20well%20through%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20people%20from%20our%20generation%20are%20going%20to%20therapy%20today%20because%20of%20what%20they%20went%20through%20as%20children.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20buildup%20of%20years%20of%20trauma.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20our%20children%20to%20go%20through%20the%20same.%20We%20want%20to%20educate%20kids%20to%20understand%20themselves%20better.%20As%20a%20single%20mother%2C%20I%20want%20my%20daughter%20to%20be%20able%20to%20differentiate%20between%20right%20and%20wrong.%20We%20also%20have%20programmes%20for%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEITA%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20a%20holistic%20solution%20for%20children.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20are%20today%20working%20in%20fields%20which%20are%20miles%20away%20from%20what%20we%20studied.%20We%20want%20this%20to%20be%20an%20early%20intervention%20for%20kids%20to%20bridge%20all%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20education%20system.%20Learning%20to%20express%20yourself%20is%20a%20very%20important%20skill%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20profession%20you%20choose%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20June%202023%2C%20the%20centre%20has%20had%20a%20phenomenal%20response%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founder.%20Their%20group%20sessions%20are%20a%20great%20hit.%20They%20have%20conducted%20sessions%20like%20%E2%80%98Her%20Canvas%3A%20Art%20Journaling%20for%20Women%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Our%20Game%20of%20Hope%E2%80%99%20(interactive%20games%20for%20adults).%20They%20are%20planning%20to%20launch%20online%20support%20groups%20on%2010%20October%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20wants%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%20to%20become%20the%20go-to%20mental%20health%20space%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20both%20offline%20and%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Comfortable%20spaces%20for%20therapy%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696427515-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1696