ation%2C%20so%20he%20would%20instead%20fill%20%3Cem%3Ebaraf%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ice%20slabs)%20and%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(salt)%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Ematka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20earthen%20pot)%20that%20would%20reduce%20temperatures%20to%20minus%20degrees.%20He%20would%20then%20set%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20contents%20in%20a%3Cem%3E%20mitti%20ka%20koonja%20%3C%2Fem%3E(clay%20earthenware)%2C%20store%20these%20in%20a%20huge%20clay%20pot%2C%20and%20then%20carry%20it%20on%20his%20head%20to%20the%20old%20Delhi%20streets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVishal%20adds%20that%20his%20great-grandfather%20would%20serve%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20on%20a%20leaf%20and%20sell%20it%20for%20four%20%3Cem%3Eannas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eeach.%20In%20a%20day%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20sell%20about%20100%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirorimal's%20son%20Mohanlal%20with%20Johnny%20Walker.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKuremal-4-1696426084-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKirorimal%E2%80%99s%20son%20Mohanlal%20with%20Johnny%20Walker.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20set%